<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِإِذْنِهَا بِلَا مَهْرٍ؛ كَعَلَى مَا شَاءَتْ، أَوْ شَاءَ فُلَانٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ لَهَا بِعَقْدٍ:</span> مَهْرُ مِثْلٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَيَسْتَقِرُّ بِدُخُولٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ مَاتَ أَحَدُهُمَا قَبْلَ دُخُولٍ وَفَرْضٍ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَرِثَهُ الآخَرُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَهَا مَهْرُ نِسَائِهَا؛ كَأُمِّهَا، وَعَمَّتِهَا، وَخَالَتِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ طُلِّقَتْ قَبْلَهُمَا:</span> لَمْ يَكُنْ لَهَا عَلَيْهِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> إِلَّا المُتْعَةُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span> بِقَدْرِ يُسْرِهِ وَعُسْرِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَيَجِبُ مَهْرُ مِثْلٍ لِمَنْ وُطِئَتْ بِشُبْهَةٍ، أَوْ زِنىً كُرْهاً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- لَا أَرْشُ بَكَارَةٍ مَعَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَلَهَا مَنْعُ نَفْسِهَا حَتَّى تَقْبِضَ مَهْراً حَالًّا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> لَا:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> إِذَا حَلَّ قَبْلَ تَسْلِيمٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> أَوْ تَبَرَّعَتْ بِتَسْلِيمِ نَفْسِهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ أَعْسَرَ بِحَالٍّ:</span> فَلَهَا الفَسْخُ بِحَاكِمٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (عليه) سقطت من (د).</p> </div>